<section class="skills" id="skills">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title glitch-text" data-text="// Skills & Profile">// Skills & Profile</h2>
    
    <div class="profile-grid">
      <div class="profile-card">
        <h3>$ whoami</h3>
        <p>Técnico en sistemas con habilidades en creación, reparación y mantenimiento de hardware y software. Experiencia práctica en desarrollo web y configuración de equipos de red (switches/routers) mediante SSH. Habilidades blandas desarrolladas como monitor académico.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="profile-card">
        <h3>$ cat objective.txt</h3>
        <p>Desarrollar, mantener y dar soporte de software, red de internet o hardware para una empresa o cliente.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Web Development</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">React</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">CSS</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">HTML</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Programming</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Java</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Python</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Networking</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Cisco (L2/L3)</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">IPv4/IPv6</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">VLAN</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">DHCP</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">NAT</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Systems & Tools</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Linux</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Windows</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">VirtualBox</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Figma</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Packet Tracer</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Security</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Firewalls</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Vulnerability Analysis</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Best Practices</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Hardware</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Assembly</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Repair</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Diagnostics</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .skills {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-matrix);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--color-matrix-primary);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.5);
    position: relative;
  }

  .glitch-text {
    position: relative;
    animation: glitch-skew 3s infinite;
  }

  .glitch-text::before,
  .glitch-text::after {
    content: attr(data-text);
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .glitch-text::before {
    left: 2px;
    text-shadow: -2px 0 var(--color-matrix-accent);
    clip: rect(44px, 450px, 56px, 0);
    animation: glitch-anim 5s infinite linear alternate-reverse;
  }

  .glitch-text::after {
    left: -2px;
    text-shadow: -2px 0 #00fff9, 2px 2px var(--color-matrix-accent);
    animation: glitch-anim2 1s infinite linear alternate-reverse;
  }

  @keyframes glitch-anim {
    0% { clip: rect(31px, 9999px, 94px, 0); }
    50% { clip: rect(90px, 9999px, 60px, 0); }
    100% { clip: rect(70px, 9999px, 10px, 0); }
  }

  @keyframes glitch-anim2 {
    0% { clip: rect(65px, 9999px, 119px, 0); }
    50% { clip: rect(82px, 9999px, 105px, 0); }
    100% { clip: rect(71px, 9999px, 8px, 0); }
  }

  @keyframes glitch-skew {
    0%, 100% { transform: skew(0deg); }
    11% { transform: skew(2deg); }
    21% { transform: skew(-1deg); }
  }

  .profile-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .profile-card {
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-matrix-primary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .profile-card:hover {
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .profile-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-matrix);
    color: var(--color-matrix-primary);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .profile-card p {
    color: #ddd;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .skill-category h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .prompt {
    color: var(--color-matrix-accent);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  .skill-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .skill-tag {
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-matrix-primary);
    color: var(--color-matrix-primary);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .skill-tag:hover {
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.3);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .skills {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
